message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $95. I think you'll find it's a great deal!
I appreciate your offer, but I was thinking more along the lines of $80.
I understand your position, Bob, but $80 is a bit too low for me. How about we meet in the middle at $87?
I appreciate your willingness to meet in the middle, but I was thinking more along the lines of $85.
